{"id": "ChIJ92PJZACBhYARNPp87Z8bTtI", "rating": 4.3, "userRatingCount": 60, "displayName": {"text": "POPMART Union Square", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJ92PJZACBhYARNPp87Z8bTtI/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25VMU1HbzJUVFl0WXpkZk9UZG5TR2RXUW5ZMGNrRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "6 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "It was my birthday and my friend strongly suggested that I get a la bubu. I didn't even know what that was. But we went and after much deliberation we got one of those little surprise boxes. I was like what the hell.\n\nThis was a super cute store. Very well organized. Very clean would definitely recommend for anyone who's into this sort of thing.\n\nIt was fun to see all the artists works. Sort of a pop art museum. Fun place to take a date or just wander around.\n\nAfterwards drop by the Nintendo store just a block up Powell for some nostalgia.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "It was my birthday and my friend strongly suggested that I get a la bubu. I didn't even know what that was. But we went and after much deliberation we got one of those little surprise boxes. I was like what the hell.\n\nThis was a super cute store. Very well organized. Very clean would definitely recommend for anyone who's into this sort of thing.\n\nIt was fun to see all the artists works. Sort of a pop art museum. Fun place to take a date or just wander around.\n\nAfterwards drop by the Nintendo store just a block up Powell for some nostalgia.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Joann Kuo", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/103372441559120123623/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUv2DKX10sh8Du3Mu7MEhAjtfZmkJWucxMGSGP7O3f9xt2Jqti0Vg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-15T06:28:23.695724413Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25VMU1HbzJUVFl0WXpkZk9UZG5TR2RXUW5ZMGNrRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25VMU1HbzJUVFl0WXpkZk9UZG5TR2RXUW5ZMGNrRRAB!2m1!1s0x8085810064c963f7:0xd24e1b9fed7cfa34"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ92PJZACBhYARNPp87Z8bTtI/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2padWNHbFVjSEV3VWpWMGFFNUdiVWx1ZWtWdmQzYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "9 months ago", "rating": 3, "text": {"text": "Im so glad I was able to visit this popmart location in union square!! It was not crowded when I arrived and the store had many figurines out on display! Sadly, they did not have that many items in stock due to it still being soft opening. However, I was able to snatch skullpandas and dimoos!!! Store has two levels but still felt a bit cramped", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Im so glad I was able to visit this popmart location in union square!! It was not crowded when I arrived and the store had many figurines out on display! Sadly, they did not have that many items in stock due to it still being soft opening. However, I was able to snatch skullpandas and dimoos!!! Store has two levels but still felt a bit cramped", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "oakinawa", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106984470328450027157/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV7IqUCvJfMgCFKk7U9h08qlXuA11b0LRWdESH3NP4vEYy74J-xwQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2025-10-10T06:34:08.267964613Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2padWNHbFVjSEV3VWpWMGFFNUdiVWx1ZWtWdmQzYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2padWNHbFVjSEV3VWpWMGFFNUdiVWx1ZWtWdmQzYxAB!2m1!1s0x8085810064c963f7:0xd24e1b9fed7cfa34"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ92PJZACBhYARNPp87Z8bTtI/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tGTk0xQjVabWRNZFd4WlVtRTBUVFpsVEZBelVYYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "6 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "Family wanted to check out the shop so waited 15 mins in line to get in.  Had a decent selection of figurines.  2 stories. Friendly staff to help and kept the crowd inside manageable so customers can walk around comfortably.  If you're a fan, worth the visit.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Family wanted to check out the shop so waited 15 mins in line to get in.  Had a decent selection of figurines.  2 stories. Friendly staff to help and kept the crowd inside manageable so customers can walk around comfortably.  If you're a fan, worth the visit.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Vinny", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109390778713616119721/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLw3r_F7N8ytzK16dQM89FqW1Bj8BRLrv1iMNr1iwX_E-VGYkTn=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2025-12-28T15:55:45.463732738Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tGTk0xQjVabWRNZFd4WlVtRTBUVFpsVEZBelVYYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tGTk0xQjVabWRNZFd4WlVtRTBUVFpsVEZBelVYYxAB!2m1!1s0x8085810064c963f7:0xd24e1b9fed7cfa34"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ92PJZACBhYARNPp87Z8bTtI/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT214ZmVVdFVZa2RvYkhWbVN6VkJTRWMyZG1rNFowRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "9 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Just visited Pop Mart in Union Square and had such a fun time! The store is bright and well-organized, making it easy to browse all the adorable collectibles. Staff was friendly and helpful when I had questions about which series to start with. Love how they display everything - really lets you see the details on each figure. Grabbed a couple blind boxes and can’t wait to see what I got. Great spot if you’re into cute toys or just want to check out something different in the area. Definitely coming back!​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Just visited Pop Mart in Union Square and had such a fun time! The store is bright and well-organized, making it easy to browse all the adorable collectibles. Staff was friendly and helpful when I had questions about which series to start with. Love how they display everything - really lets you see the details on each figure. Grabbed a couple blind boxes and can’t wait to see what I got. Great spot if you’re into cute toys or just want to check out something different in the area. Definitely coming back!​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Rhett Burden", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106820082273099522485/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVT1lzSH2DbOG-ONZoV-pmyQjqeMQBJgD3xjISwodsbKyxar04Itg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2025-10-03T00:05:52.255875219Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT214ZmVVdFVZa2RvYkhWbVN6VkJTRWMyZG1rNFowRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT214ZmVVdFVZa2RvYkhWbVN6VkJTRWMyZG1rNFowRRAB!2m1!1s0x8085810064c963f7:0xd24e1b9fed7cfa34"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ92PJZACBhYARNPp87Z8bTtI/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21zM2RqbHpXblZXUmpZMVZ6SmFRbU15VEdrMGVuYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Double storey pop mart in the heart of union square. Spacious and has helpful staff. Carries the full range of pop mart collectables including some rare collectables. Stop by for a look", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Double storey pop mart in the heart of union square. Spacious and has helpful staff. Carries the full range of pop mart collectables including some rare collectables. Stop by for a look", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttrib